      <title>Springbok 橄榄球队版权所有者将投票决定是否将股权出售给 Ackerley</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/springbok-rugby-rights-owners-to-vote-on-stake-sale-to-ackerley</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责管理卫冕世界冠军跳羚队的南非橄榄球协会 (SA Rugby) 表示，其成员工会将于 10 月 17 日投票决定将新成立的商业权利公司 20% 的股份出售给阿克利体育集团 (Ackerley Sports Group)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/springbok-rugby-rights-owners-to-vote-on-stake-sale-to-ackerley</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 11:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
